<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>내부 구성원 인증</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/auth/verify-internal-member.css" />
        <link
            rel="stylesheet"
            href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200"
        />
    </head>
    <body>
        <script>
            (function() {
                const savedTheme = localStorage.getItem('theme') || 'light';
                document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', savedTheme);
            })();
        </script>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="mypage-header">
                <h1 class="title">내부 구성원 인증</h1>
                <a onclick="history.back()" class="back-button">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_back</span>
                    이전으로 돌아가기
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="info-text">
                내부 구성원 인증을 위해 아래 정보를 입력해주세요.
            </div>

            <form class="verify-form" id="verify-form">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="verification-code">인증 코드</label>
                    <input
                        type="text"
                        id="verification-code"
                        name="key"
                        placeholder="인증 코드를 입력하세요"
                        required
                    />
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="verify-button">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">verified</span>
                    인증하기
                </button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <div class="notice-container"></div>

        <script type="module" src="/auth/verify-internal-member.mjs"></script>
    </body>
</html>
